premise_source_doc_sentence: It received numerous accolades , including Academy Award nominations for Best Original Screenplay and Best Film Editing .
The memento pattern is implemented with three objects : the originator , a caretaker and a memento .
The film 's script was based on a pitch by Jonathan Nolan , who later wrote the story `` Memento Mori '' from the concept .

Memento is presented as two different sequences of scenes interspersed during the film : a series in black-and-white that is shown chronologically , and a series of color sequences shown in reverse order  (  simulating for the audience the mental state of the protagonist  )  .
Memento premiered on September 5 , 2000 , at the Venice International Film Festival and was released in European theaters starting in October .
